{"tid":2077403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【加速】深圳公佈重建皇崗2022落成一地兩檢口岸","createTime":"2020-06-24T09:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T09:40:10.000Z","uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07e5b33098d5f146d941813c0a0e1cee4c394a8b","tid":2077403,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"深圳市口岸辦昨日公佈將會重建皇崗口岸，屆時新口岸將會以「一地兩檢」設為純旅檢口岸，並會取消貨檢功能，預計會於2022年底建成。目前旅客若從皇崗口岸入境深圳，需要先從香港的落馬洲口岸過關，屬於「兩地兩檢」的安排，惟皇崗口岸將重建為「一地兩檢」的口岸，屬深圳市單方面宣告，港府直到現時仍然未有公佈任何消息及詳情，亦未知屆時落馬洲出入境大樓有何安排。<br />\n<br />\n根據深圳市口岸辦網站顯示，新口岸會在旅檢區的原址重建，項目於去年6月正式啟動，首先會在貨驗區建設臨時旅檢場地，之後會拆除皇崗口岸片區的老舊建築，最後再建設新口岸，目前首階段工作已經完成，昨正式啟用臨時旅檢大樓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7xzfAh8zSZzdIVLYy-sbyb8PAaQ=/802x451/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GK65EEJBASS6VPIYLXSMDKIUFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7xzfAh8zSZzdIVLYy-sbyb8PAaQ%3D%2F802x451%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGK65EEJBASS6VPIYLXSMDKIUFY.jpg&h=09f2164a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果，請click link:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/383uz0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F383uz0w&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=733c6f8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/383uz0w</a>"},{"pid":"2231303d10a827355ff97ac1faab294a17b683aa","tid":2077403,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=ce814d35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"b3092806e0c6728e6a139bde58278b838e0adbd3","tid":2077403,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a50975bb821685e64cdcdcf2f7fa9260521e13a","tid":2077403,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"想知道重建完成後經皇崗口岸北上飲喜茶食海底撈會慳左幾多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a95ff87e66b3af229514077b917d3d143c4e32","tid":2077403,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:39:30.000Z","msg":"拆左佢咪算囉<br />\n又送錢畀中國洗"},{"pid":"70b4358ddd421e6a49c7895325738eb9ed110b14","tid":2077403,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"要去沙灣call g了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}